\">【答案解析】本药抑制细胞内二氢叶酸还原酶</span>,使嘌呤合成受抑,同时具抗炎作用。不良反应有肝损害、胃肠道反应、骨髓抑制和口炎等,停药后多能恢复。利妥昔单抗：主要用于治疗复发或化疗耐药的B淋巴细胞型非霍奇金淋巴瘤。来氟米特：主要抑制合成嘧啶的二氢乳清酸脱氢酶,使活化淋巴细胞的生长受抑。与甲氨蝶呤有协同作用，常联合使用。主要不良反应有胃肠道反应、肝损伤、骨髓抑制和脱发等。布洛芬：非甾体抗炎药：通过抑制环氧化酶(COX),从而抑制花生四烯酸转化为前列腺素,起到抗炎、解热、镇痛的效果。该药应用广泛,起效快,镇痛效果好，但不能控制原发病的病情进展。&nbsp;</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":7151,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","updateTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","isTrue":false,"questionId":2574,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">利妥昔单抗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7152,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","updateTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","isTrue":false,"questionId":2574,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">来氟米特</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7153,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","updateTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","isTrue":true,"questionId":2574,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">甲氨蝶呤</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7154,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","updateTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","isTrue":false,"questionId":2574,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">布洛芬</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7155,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","updateTime":"2019-06-20 16:10:13","isTrue":false,"questionId":2574,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">羟氯喹</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1260,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1025,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2571,"createT