e:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">特异性高，但与</span>SLE活动性无关</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【答案解析】抗</span>Sm抗体: 诊断SLE的标记抗体之一。特异性99%,但敏感性仅25%,有助于早期和不典型患者的诊断或回顾性诊断。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":7016,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2547,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">抗核抗体</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7017,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","isTrue":true,"questionId":2547,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">抗</span>Sm抗体</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7018,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2547,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">抗双链</span>DNA抗体</span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7019,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2547,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">抗磷酯抗体</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":7020,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:57:59","isTrue":false,"questionId":2547,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">类风湿因子</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1260,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1025,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2537,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","topicId":null,"tagId":1025,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":6,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">痛风</span></span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【答案解析】</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">急性关节炎是原发性痛风的最常见首发症状。初发时往往为单一关节受累</span>,继之累及多个关节。以蹲趾的跖趾关节为好发部位，其次为足底、踝、足跟、膝、腕指和肘。第一次发作通常在夜间,数小时内出现红肿、热及明显压痛,关节迅速肿胀,伴发热、白细胞增多与血沉增快等全身症状。疼痛较剧烈,压痛明显,患者常在夜间痛醒而难以忍受。受寒、劳累、酗酒、食物过敏、进富含嘌呤食物、感染、创伤和手术等为常见诱因。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6966,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2537,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">颊部蝶形皮疹及蛋白尿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6967,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2537,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">腕、掌指、近指关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6968,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2537,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">膝关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6969,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","isTrue":true,"questionId":2537,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">第一趾较剧烈疼痛</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6970,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:51:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2537,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">大量龋齿提示</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1260,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1025,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2535,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","topicId":null,"tagId":1025,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":5,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">类风湿性关节炎</span>(RA)</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【答案解析】</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\">(1) 好发于中年女性。好发于手足小关节，尤其是近侧指间关节、掌指及;跖趾关节，其次为腕、肘、膝关节等。最初仅累及1~2个小关节，呈游走性，以后发展为多发性和对称性关节炎。(2)发病缓慢而渐进，病变发作与缓解交替出现，病程可长达数年至数十年;关节疼痛、肿胀，活动受限，多关节受累;最后关节活动极度受限，甚至发生半脱位，畸形或强直。同时伴有不规则发热、体重减轻、脉搏增快、贫血、血沉加快、白细胞数增高等全身表现。(3)晨僵现象:经常出现晨起时典型的关节僵硬，全身发紧，活动后缓解。体格检查足小关节或受累关节对称性肿胀、畸形或强直，关节功能受限。X线表现:早期仅见软组织肿胀，以后出现骨质疏松，关节间隙变窄，关节面边缘侵蚀及骨质内小囊状破坏，可发生关节畸形和骨性强直。多数活动期患者有轻至中度正细胞性贫血,白细胞数大多正常,有时可见嗜酸性粒细胞和血小板增多,血清免疫球蛋白IgG、 IgM、IgA可升高,血清补体水平多数正常或轻度升高,60%~80%患者有高水平类风湿因子(RF),但RF阳性也见于慢性感染(肝炎、结核等)、其他结缔组织病和正常老年人。其他如抗角质蛋白抗体(AKA)、抗核周因子(APF)和抗环瓜氨酸多肽(CCP)等自身抗体对类风湿关节炎有较高的诊断特异性,敏感性在30%~40%左右。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6956,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","isTrue":false,"questionId":2535,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">颊部蝶形皮疹及蛋白尿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6957,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","isTrue":true,"questionId":2535,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">腕、掌指、近指关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6958,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","isTrue":false,"questionId":2535,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">膝关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6959,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","isTrue":false,"questionId":2535,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">第一趾较剧烈疼痛</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6960,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:50:52","isTrue":false,"questionId":2535,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">大量龋齿提示</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1260,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1025,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2533,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","topicId":null,"tagId":1025,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":4,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">系统性红斑狼疮</span>(SLE)</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【答案解析】</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">系统性红斑狼疮诊断：</span>1.颊部红斑——固定红斑,扁平或高起,在两颧突出部位。2.盘状红斑——片状高起于皮肤的红斑,粘附有角质脱屑和毛囊栓;陈旧病变可发生萎缩性瘢痕。3.光过敏——对日光有明显的反应,引起皮疹，从病史中得知或医生观察到。4.口腔溃疡——经医生观察到的口腔或鼻咽部溃疡,一般为无痛性。5.关节炎——非侵蚀性关节炎,累及2个或更多的外周关节,有压痛,肿胀或积液。6.浆膜炎——胸膜炎或心包炎。7.肾脏病变——尿蛋白＞0.5g/24h或+++,或管型(红细胞、血红蛋白、颗粒或混合管型)。8.神经病变——癫痫发作或精神病,除外药物或已知的代谢紊乱。9.血液学疾病——溶血性贫血，或白细胞减少，或淋巴细胞减少,，或血小板减少。10.免疫学异常——抗dsDNA抗体阳性,或抗Sm抗体阳性,或抗磷脂抗体阳性(包括抗心磷脂抗体、或狼疮抗凝物、或至少持续6个月的梅毒血清试验假阳性三者中具备一项阳性)。11.抗核抗体——在任何时候和未用药物诱发“药物性狼疮”的情况下,抗核抗体滴度异常。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6946,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","isTrue":true,"questionId":2533,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">颊部蝶形皮疹及蛋白尿</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6947,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2533,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">腕、掌指、近指关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6948,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2533,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">膝关节受累</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6949,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2533,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">第一趾较剧烈疼痛</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6950,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","updateTime":"2019-06-20 15:49:36","isTrue":false,"questionId":2533,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">大量龋齿提示</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1260,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","updateTime":"2019-06-09 15:52:30","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":54},{"id":1025,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:53:33","name":"风湿B1","questionCnt":20,"tagTypeId":48}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2531,"createTime":"2019-06-20 15:48:31","topicId":null,"tagId":1025,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":3,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">干燥综合征</span>(SS)</span></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\"